NAME
    EV::Websockets - WebSocket client/server using libwebsockets and EV

SYNOPSIS
    See lib/EV/Websockets.pm for full documentation and usage examples.

INSTALLATION
    To install this module, run the following commands:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

DEPENDENCIES
    This module requires:
    - EV
    - Alien::libwebsockets (v4.3.3+)

